<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>rtorrent cheat sheet</title>
	</head>

<body bgcolor=#111111>
	<p style="color:green;font-family:monospace;font-size:10px">
		<code>
		Main View
		---------------------
		^q             - quit
		bksp           - add torrent
		->             - view download
		1 - 7          - change view
		^S             - start download
		^D             - stop download (or remove stopped download)
		^K             - close a torrent
		+ / -          - change priority

		Trottling
		--------------------
		a / s / d      - increase upload throttle by 1 / 5 / 10 KB
		z / x / c      -  decrease upload throttle by 1 / 5 / 10 KB
		A / S / D      - increase download throttle by 1 / 5 / 10 KB
		Z / X / C      - decrease download throttle by 1 / 5 / 10 KB
		</code>
	</p>
</body>
</html>